	this file contains the presets for system auto config.
	The presets are organised in the same way as the options.xml 
	file in the game folder.
	The tags are organised like this:
	<graphicsPreferences> HIGH       // Name of the preset
		<GPUMemory>800</GPUMemory>   // minimum total GPU Memory
		<RAM>4000</RAM>              // minimum RAM amount
	</graphicsPreferences>
	
	-->

